title: DPS BestOf

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the Lakers enlisting the help of Phil Jackson as a look for a new Head Coach. Dan shares an idea to get attendance up as A's games. And Sean Salisbury discusses why Ryan Tannehill is right when he says it's not his job to mentor Malik Willis.
